<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Job Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 32px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }
    .email-header {
      background-color: #2563eb;
      padding: 28px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .email-body {
      padding: 32px 24px;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #374151;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .info-box h2 {
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
      color: #2563eb;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .info-box p {
      margin: 4px 0;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 32px;
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #9ca3af;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .email-footer a {
      color: #2563eb;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>🎉 New Job Alert!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="email-body">
      <p class="greeting">Hi <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>

      <p>Great news! <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>, a company you're following, has just posted a new job opening that might interest you.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h2>{{jobName}}</h2>
        <p><strong>Company:</strong> {{companyName}}</p>
        <p>This opportunity could be the perfect next step in your career journey!</p>
      </div>

      <p>Don't miss out on this exciting opportunity. Click the button below to view the full job details and apply:</p>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
        <a href="{{jobDetailUrl}}" class="cta-button">View Job Details</a>
      </div>

      <p style="color: #6b7280;">
        <em>This email was sent because you're following {{companyName}}. Want to manage your notifications? Log in to your account to update your preferences.</em>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} IT Job Portal. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        <a href="#">Unsubscribe</a> |
        <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> |
        <a href="#">Contact Us</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
